title: Neenah Astrobrights Laser, Inkjet Print Printable Multipurpose Card, Blue, 65lb
description: Astrobrights Colored Cardstock is high-impact paper that features bold, deeply saturated colors to make your creations stand out. Its 65 lb. paper weight makes it the perfect choice for flyers, school projects, direct mail and much more. It is acid-free and lignin-free for long-lasting color yet it is smooth enough to work with inkjet and laser printers. Don't worry about expensive ink for full color prints. Use brighter colors for brighter ideas.
